{"tid":1545273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9.6今晚太子站攞片　揾真‧春袋　唔出嚟同藍絲無分別","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:33:51.000Z","uid":110703,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f541ee068454066cfb66b59153ea22eb6ddedd4b","tid":1545273,"uid":110703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:46:18.000Z","msg":"8.31恐襲CCTV攞片最後機會係今晚<br />\n今晚一過　有義士死咗都死無對證　所以求下大家出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係　要攞片　唔係９企　同防暴、狗屋對峙、鳩屌佢地就有用<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再相信黨鐵　唔撚會主動交片之餘　今晚一人多一定已經全部防暴進駐　甚至封站<br />\n所以要攞片　就要自己攞　至於點攞　交俾大家</span></span><br />\n真係做唔到啲咩既　９企俾壓力popo　唔出嚟既話同班藍絲活在自己世界　只要唔係攪到自己就乜都唔理無分別<br />\n求求大家　港版６．４極有可能已能上演　真相唔掘唔會自己出嚟　<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今晚攞到片　還義士清白之餘　場運動係會180度扭轉　喺強弩之末之下變成炮彈</span></span></strong><br />\n求求大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eeb7f6760aff251e4fd15e5847584be00d44698","tid":1545273,"uid":266362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"